name: 4chDemoPL2.pl2
citation: Hussein, Kareem (2023) 4chDemoPL2.pl2 (Version draft) [Data set]. DANDI archive. https://dandiarchive.org/dandiset/000726/draft
description:
PL2 file with 4 individual channels of sorted spikes, continuous wideband, and continuous field potentials. 16 channels of events. One channel of strobed data that increments in value from 32513 to 32767. One channel of auxiliary analog input.
Source: https://plexon.com/software-downloads/#software-downloads-data-samples
